orm=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">ἐκ πολλοῦ</ref></xr>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">long ago;</tr_> but the passage is prob. corrupt. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n35983.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἕνη καὶ νέα</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἡμέρα</foreign>) <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the old and new day,</tr_> i.e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">the last day of the month,</tr_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12.374.276</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg003.perseus-grc1:1134s\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nu.\">Nu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1134s</biblScope> </bibl>q., <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0540.tlg023.perseus-grc1:6\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lys.\">Lys.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.6</biblScope> </bibl>: first used by Solon, acc. to <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0004.tlg001.perseus-grc1:1:57\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.L.\">D.L.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.57</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">Σκιροφοριῶνος ἕνῃ καὶ νέᾳ</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IG\">IG</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.916.10</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. Decr. ap. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0014.tlg018.perseus-grc1:29\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.\">D.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">18.29